{cls, fgbg 2 0}
Welcome to the {fg 3}Yellow Toaster BBS,{fg 2} using{fg 2} Converse BBS software,
a Bulletin Board System server designed for RISC OS.

Converse is programmed in C, supports modern features and is {flash 1}Open Source!{flash 0}
It is designed to be {fg 1}user-friendly{fg 3}, {fg 3}versatile{fg 2} and {fg 7}expandable{fg 3}.

You can find out more at https://www.github.com/andrewtimmins/riscos-converse

{fg 2,flash 1}Please mail the sysop if you're interested in running an Converse system!{flash 0}

{fg 3}The time is %{time} and the date is %{date}.
{fg 2}You have used %{todaytime} minutes so far today.
{fg 3}You have logged on %{usercalls} times.
{fg 2}You last called on %{lastlogon}.
{fg 3}Your user-level is %{accesslevel}, and your usernumber is #%{userid}

{fg 6}You are using Converse version %{version}.

{fg 3,}Please read the latest news from the Main Menu...

{
    if %{userprotocol} == 0 then
        print `Your default protocol is XMODEM\r\n`
    else
        if %{userprotocol} == 1 then
            print `Your default protocol is XMODEM-CRC\r\n`
        else
            if %{userprotocol} == 2 then
                print `Your default protocol is XMODEM-1K\r\n`
            else
                if %{userprotocol} == 3 then
                    print `Your default protocol is YMODEM\r\n`
                else
                    if %{userprotocol} == 4 then
                        print `Your default protocol is YMODEM-G\r\n`
                    else
                        print `Your default protocol is ZMODEM\r\n`
                    end if
                end if
            end if
        end if
    end if
}

{anykey}
